    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h1>About Lendo</h1>
        <p>Welcome to Lendo! We are dedicated to providing the best library management services to our community. Our
            mission is to ensure a seamless experience for users in accessing and managing library resources.</p>
        <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p>Our project is based on the "sharing is caring" theory. Here, people in need can raise their requests for any
            item, and those who own such items can accept the requests to lend them free of cost. This way, people will
            be able to obtain urgently needed items within the campus.</p>
        <p>This entire process does not involve money; instead, it operates on a point-based system. To be eligible to
            request an item, you need certain points, which you can earn by lending your items to others. In this way,
            your generous actions will not only help others but also become your reward.</p>
